# Brain Widget

Remix-compatible React component for the Brain trading companion prototype.

## Dependency

```bash
npm install @lottiefiles/dotlottie-react
```

## Usage

Render this component below the application's 48px header:

```tsx
import { BrainWidget } from "~/packages/brain";

export default function BrainRoute() {
  return <BrainWidget />;
}
```

The component owns `height: calc(100vh - 48px)`. All component styling is supplied through React `style` props. Static assets live under `public/brain/` and use absolute `/brain/...` URLs.
